fields.name: ASUS ZenBook Flip 14 UX461UA
fields.description: There's nothing ordinary about the gorgeous ZenBook Flip 14, but there's a whole lot of extraordinary. For a start, ZenBook Flip 14 is a creative powerhouse that's breathtakingly thin and unbelievably light, with the added versatility of a 360°-flippable touchscreen and ASUS Pen support to take you beyond the boundaries of a traditional laptop. With its 8th Generation Intel® Core™ i7 quad-core processor, ZenBook Flip 14 gives you the raw power to effortlessly do whatever you need to do, and to do it quicker. Whether you want on-the-go creativity in tablet mode, portable document-crunching in laptop mode, or stress-busting relaxation in whatever mode, the powerful, versatile and creative ZenBook Flip 14 does it all, with extraordinarily refined elegance and style.
